data.description: Beautiful home resting on 5 level acres of land. 3 Br/2 Ba with zoned bedrooms and an inviting open floor plan! Upgraded trim work with electric fireplace accented in shiplap. Home recently remodeled with many upgraded features. The outdoors features a large deck, above ground pool, approx 4.5 acres with a 4 stall horse barn, tack room, wash rack, hay loft, electricity and hot&cold water- Also has a pond! Don’t miss out on this great property with so much to offer!!
